"39:74:16" : {s: 39, a: 74, w: 16, r: "عمل", t: "ٱلْعَٰمِلِينَ", l: "عَٰمِل", lc: 12, tl: "l-ʿāmilīna", lb: "কাজ করা,আমল করা",e: "(of) the workers", b: "কর্ম সম্পাদনকারীগণের", f: 3, rm: "to do/make/act/work/operate/perform/construct/manufacture, practice a handcraft, be active, one who does."},
